title: Bengals-Browns MNF Recap + Top 6 RBs in the NFL right now

description:
Gregg Rosenthal is joined by the one and only Nick Wesseling to recap the Bengals at Browns Monday Night Football matchup. Then, Gregg gives his list of the six best pure runners in the NFL based solely on the 2022 season with the help of Nick and Gravedigger.
